e. Still, B's weaknesses are pretentiousness and wrong tone, which affect crew. A's unfriendly also similar. D's moody/loner also similar. C's communication difficulty and egocentric also similar. All have some. Which weakness is less severe? Pretentiousness and wrong tone may be less severe than being unfriendly? Hard to say. Also B's strengths directly relevant to long-distance: stress handling, weather assessment, conscientiousness. I'd provisionally prefer B.\n\nWe should note uncertainties: we lack info on actual teamwork performance, training, health beyond eating habits. If other agents have additional strengths for other candidates, could change.\n\nThus provisional vote B.\n\nNow produce output."}
